definitions.text:
[đỡ đầu] to sponsor 
 Đỡ đầu cho một đứa trẻ (trong lễ rửa tội ) 
 To act as godfather/godmother to a child; 
 To stand sponsor to a child; 
 To sponsor a child

@đỡ lời
- Answer in another's stead, answer on another's behalf
=Tôi xin đỡ lời cụ tôi cảm ơn ông+I wish to thank you on behalf of my grandfather

@đỡ nhẹ
- (thông tục) Relieve someone of
=Bị đỡ nhẹ mất cái bút máy+To be relieved of one's fountain-pen
